snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: xRavenXP

This is a longplay of a plataform game Sonic The Hedgehog 2 (Game Gear version).
Tails is kidnapped by Dr. Eggman and Sonic must rescue him. Is a good 8-bit version of Sonic too. The run includes all chaos emeralds collected!
